OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'It took me 57 years to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffind my baby's grave'      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In May, BBC North West Tonight told the
OL,6, story of Lilian Thorpe, a woman who had
OL,7, never known where or even if her       
OL,8, stillborn baby had been buried.        
OL,10,FIn the programme, the council which    
OL,11,Fhelped Lilian find her son encouraged  
OL,12,Fothers in a similar situation to access
OL,13,Frecords by providing the mother's full 
OL,14,Fname at the time of the birth, their   
OL,15,Faddress and the date of their baby's   
OL,16,Fdeath.                                 
OL,18,FAnne Howard and Gina Jacobs were two   
OL,19,Fsuch women and were spurred into action
OL,20,Fafter seeing Lilian's story.           
